T="1 letter">ment is in <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> wherein the Souls of men are concerned. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Generation wherein they Live will certain|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> be either much the better, or much the wor&s;e <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> them. If they are corrupt, they will be <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">rupters of the Generation. <HI>From the Pro|phets
